description: Updates a group, or batch, of vehicles. For more information, see Update multiple vehicles (AWS CLI) in the Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise Developer Guide.

nested_items.name: vehicles
nested_items.description: A list of information about the batch of updated vehicles.

nested_items.name: vehicleName
nested_items.description: The unique ID of the updated vehicle.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the updated vehicle.

nested_items.name: errors
nested_items.description: A list of information about errors returned while updating a batch of vehicles, or, if there aren't any errors, an empty list.

nested_items.name: vehicleName
nested_items.description: The ID of the vehicle with the error.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: A message associated with the error.
